welcome_message_body: "Welcome to North St. Paul, a charming city known for its rich history and friendly community. We invite you to explore our unique shops and restaurants, and enjoy all that our beautiful city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport offers a variety of amenities and services for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: For those flying on private jets, the private terminal at Downtown Airport provides a luxurious and exclusive experience.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Flying Cloud Airport caters to private and corporate flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, primarily serving low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport offers domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Crystal Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Crystal Airport is exclusively for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
